Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:14.36,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:15.32,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.13,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He passed one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:19.09,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He's in fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:22.83,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,He passed another!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:23.75,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Third!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.22,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:28.30,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:32.05,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,And another! He's in second! Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:33.67,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He's closing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:36.51,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,They're dead even!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.98,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.98,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.98,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Haruka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:51.32,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,We
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:53.85,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,won!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.77,Board,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Samezuka Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.77,Board2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Iwatobi High School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:06.67,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, that was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:07.95,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:10.00,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-senpai, that was truly inspiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:12.19,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my heart was racing just watching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:14.29,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Same here! Mine's {\i1}still{\i0} racing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.09,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We actually get to go to regionals!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:22.76,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:24.28,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:25.80,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.18,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.62,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:28.73,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:28.73,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:33.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:07.29,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Despite being a brand-new club,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:09.78,EpTitle,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(438,508)}Hesitant Loosen Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}our swimmers placed in \Nthe top 8 at prefecturals
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:13.36,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and qualified for regionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:17.85,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We hope that they're able \Nto advance to nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:18.99,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:23.95,Banner,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations to the Swim Club \Non Making Regionals
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:23.30,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,They were really ready for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.60,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that they reused an old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.12,Banner,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Swim Club
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:25.97,Banner,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Judo Club
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.71,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,But it's finally starting \Nto sink in that we won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:30.60,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.19,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,They'll treat us like heroes \Nwhen we enter the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.37,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.19,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, Hana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.78,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hanging out with boys, huh? \NTrue to your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.91,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,We won?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:36.51,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:37.28,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What do you mean, you don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.40,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about how \NGou has a boyish name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and hangs out with boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.32,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:12.06,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.01,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:13.98,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.32,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Haruka-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.61,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He wandered off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:26.95,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Did he go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.41,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he does this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.90,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we've accomplished our \Nobjective of placing at a tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.39,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,so they should give us a bigger budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.96,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,And we can use that budget to \Nswim at a gym all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.62,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.07,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:39.92,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.32,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening to the principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:45.56,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Our next objective is to \Nmake it to nationals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:45.92,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.86,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Always aim high!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.68,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.72,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best to make it to nationals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.37,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.43,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:55.67,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,...high!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.31,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the first one in the club room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.32,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.26,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can beat a former \Ntrack and field athlete?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.72,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:05.82,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.82,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,We'll mainly be running drills for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.86,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Rei-kun, you'll work on your kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:14.46,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be training to develop \Na faster and stronger kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:16.34,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:19.34,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa-kun, you'll focus on \Nstrengthening your crawl stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.34,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:24.54,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto-senpai, you need to work on \Nmaking your acceleration more even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.55,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.14,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start warming up then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:28.64,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.45,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.56,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You were already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:39.00,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:39.81,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.55,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan's really motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.94,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How long have you been swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.37,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's upset about losing at free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.62,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Not very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:48.69,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's hot out today, so I brought \Nice to keep your drinks cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.41,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:49.41,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:53.86,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to see you so motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:54.79,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.96,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I was swimming because I \Ndidn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:06.24,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I should ask the water \Nabout matters involving water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.93,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.16,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone's here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.25,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:14.66,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:17.16,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Then everybody should \Nstart by warming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.10,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.10,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.20,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No running!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:33.45,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you're swimming well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.28,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.77,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,You posted a personal best \Nduring the group stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.63,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,so it looks like your decision to \Nfocus on the 100m free paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.88,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to make it to the final.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.44,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.52,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.15,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do everything I can to support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.78,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.37,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:58.78,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:02.98,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,You were so happy about \Nbeating Nanase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:05.77,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:10.11,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can move on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.91,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry up. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.03,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.04,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.68,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,We're off to pray for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:22.79,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.42,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Hachiman-sama's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:25.98,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.79,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, there's a summer \Nfestival for Hachiman-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:30.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.98,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be lots of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:32.72,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:37.17,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine also hosts a festival \Nfor the god of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.92,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We should pay a visit before regionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.10,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,If that's okay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.98,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rei-chan's waiting for you to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.23,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,The four of us must go together, \Nor there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.43,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,His words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.23,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Was that supposed to be a Rei impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:50.94,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.27,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.66,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.91,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.10,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.24,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.76,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Good one, Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.49,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan, Haru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.29,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,If you arrive early for a date, \Nthat's what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.34,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.84,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's visit the shrine first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:17.81,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.77,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.43,Station,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Iwatobi Station
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.59,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fan of yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.44,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,We should have worn ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:29.90,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I believe you're familiar \Nwith this area, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.08,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.08,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:31.98,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:33.23,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:35.11,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how much money did they give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.96,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I got a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:38.92,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We have to try candy apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.77,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I wanna play shooting games!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.84,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.50,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Candy apples come first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.69,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Squid! Squid! Squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.38,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Candy apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.38,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:53.23,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, there's squid everywhere, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.02,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.68,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Just squiddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.10,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,So where should we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.06,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.92,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Squid Catching Heaven is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:05.84,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of weird event is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:08.11,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:08.59,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:09.38,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.38,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You should participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.40,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.49,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds so... slimy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:14.44,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.49,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.39,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the event's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.57,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.23,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.18,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, we don't want to lose \Nsight of Nagisa and Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.04,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.47,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It went your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.50,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.00,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.44,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.67,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You can still join in, Rei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.44,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.85,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Mako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.28,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.06,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:43.21,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Gou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.14,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.62,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing yukata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.13,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You both look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.47,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,You mean just our yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:53.28,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.00,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Should we grab something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:56.80,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.06,Main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend the squid paella.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:09:59.95,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:04.08,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll be watching the \NSquid Ink Calligraphy Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.96,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.89,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.50,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We have to start with fried squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.65,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I want squid tempura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.26,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look around then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.56,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I could go for some paella.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.22,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go through the stalls first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.53,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:28.00,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to walk around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.36,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,However, don't get into any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:30.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:33.76,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, let's look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.11,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.12,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Squid burgers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.66,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested in trying out squid and chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:46.90,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to get lost, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:47.83,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:51.23,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Rei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.55,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.44,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Bad timing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.38,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.43,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:07.55,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we were wondering how many \Nbowls of squid we can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.59,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's try a shooting game!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.34,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to eat that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:09.85,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:15.27,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'll go buy squid burgers for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.95,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,How thoughtful of you, Nagisa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.04,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.77,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wait in the rest area over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:23.41,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I don't want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.95,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Er, but we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.12,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go then, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.14,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find space for all four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.32,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:42.24,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that Rin-chan and \NHaru-chan will run into each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.49,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.63,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I invited Haru-chan to the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to take his mind off swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.77,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,But it may end up having \Nthe opposite effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:53.22,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What? He might ditch the relay at regionals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.69,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the worst case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.36,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I want Haru-chan to swim with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.79,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to swim with Haruka-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.71,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to make sure they don't meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:03.72,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.67,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.92,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You follow Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:06.60,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.14,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me where Rin-chan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:12.29,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can lead Haru-chan somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.54,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa-kun, you seem to be enjoying this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.29,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Go to it, Detective Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.44,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You bought a lot of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.00,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.60,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.18,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He ran into an acquaintance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.16,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,and they're walking around \Nthe festival together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.10,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.47,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:32.73,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.87,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You stay here, Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.92,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.79,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.08,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It might be more than you can carry by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.61,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here, Haru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.95,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,So what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.20,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Rin-chan's here at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.30,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Rin's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:53.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so Rei-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:54.83,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,following him right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.62,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Target's height is estimated to be 177 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.53,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Weight is estimated to be 68 kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.64,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,He has red hair and pointy teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.97,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Commence pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.89,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Mikoshiba bought cotton candy, \Nchocolate bananas, and candy apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.48,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't expect him to enjoy those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.92,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.22,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.28,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.28,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.14,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I want that game console!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.87,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.05,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan, can you hold this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:36.75,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:41.68,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The target is currently walking \Nthrough the stalls by the beach{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:44.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and heading for the main road, over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.21,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.21,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.41,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,The closest one would be in the \Nconvenience store on the main road.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:49.97,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.03,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.22,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hold it in a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.30,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.37,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there might be a \Nporta potty over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.48,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It should be closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:13:59.73,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:01.16,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:08.15,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any stalls over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.37,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.69,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.51,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.25,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.89,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It works better if you don't try as hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:42.89,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:43.90,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:44.32,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Just like in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.65,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, it doesn't work \Nunless you try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.46,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.68,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.65,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So many!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.33,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.91,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You can have them if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.53,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.16,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.79,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We can show them off to \NTa-chan and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.70,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:02.92,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan, Mako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.92,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan's in the park in the third district.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.93,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,The park in the third district?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.18,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That leads to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.27,Elementary,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwatobi Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:17.31,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,An elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:47.17,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.01,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.45,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.33,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.49,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Makoto,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.49,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:16.55,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Faster! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:17.72,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.68,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.12,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.63,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.63,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.63,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Haruka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.25,Text,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,From: Hazuki Nagisa\NTo: Ryugazaki Rei\NWhere are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.62,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had candy apples in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.32,Text 2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,From: Rei-chan\NIwatobi Elementary School.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:06.85,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.12,Text 2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,From: Rei-chan\NSub: Untitled\NBut I lost sight of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:10.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.58,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then Rin-chan could still be—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.47,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.39,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Haru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:21.04,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Rin is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:22.79,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.29,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:29.90,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Tell Rei to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.71,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:38.67,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get Rei-chan then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.28,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.01,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.31,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:13.42,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get to prepare for that \Nrelay, so I got a bit frantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.33,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Swimming as hard as I could so \Nthe next person could go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.87,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,But in the process, I remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.08,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,what we saw that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:32.55,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy to swim in a relay \Nwith you, with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:39.82,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.14,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,not so sure anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:48.09,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a reason to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.77,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to feel the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.88,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've always believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.18,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:57.58,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,When I lost to him, \Neverything became dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.41,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,This means I'll never swim with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:02.67,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.29,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,swim with Rin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.82,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't care about anything at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.23,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Not the tournament or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.62,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,But then I watched you guys swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:25.97,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "I trained hard with these guys."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:30.06,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I might end up being \Nnothing more than filler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:31.99,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:35.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,if you guys really wanted \Nto swim in a relay,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.03,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I would swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.89,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.27,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,how it felt to swim in the \Nsame lane together,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:52.22,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,how it felt when everyone was \Nwaiting at the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.70,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It made me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.53,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,just as happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:04.81,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:06.97,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.72,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.22,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,When did you guys get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.36,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You have your answer, Haruka-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.73,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:17.99,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:19.76,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.60,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to swim in the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.74,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to swim with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:27.66,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.03,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.00,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:37.98,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That means we have to start training \Nhard tomorrow to make nationals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.37,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:42.57,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We should head home so \Nwe're ready tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.45,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,No, one last thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:45.71,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.51,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed, Haruka-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.87,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really have these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:51.60,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:53.77,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who's \Nlikely to take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.49,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.93,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you name them as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:58.77,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Name them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.04,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Just go with Nagisa, Rei, \NHaruka, and Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.42,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.98,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Mackerel, Bonito, Tuna, Jackfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.27,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:10.29,Station 2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Iwatobi Station
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.93,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:16.22,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,The train's about to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:21.50,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.06,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:34.56,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's swimming in \Nthe relay at regionals!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.81,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:13.85,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that sukiyaki looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:15.73,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Whose idea was it to have sukiyaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:18.53,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,And why in the middle of summer \Nwhen it's over 39 degrees Celsius?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.53,0:23:20.11,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,To build up stamina for the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:21.46,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nagisa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:22.91,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That hasn't been cooked enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:23.86,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little won't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:25.21,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Haruka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:27.37,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to add \Nmackerel to sukiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:29.80,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! You guys stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.71,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Irritated Heart Rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:35.92,NextEp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(528,1)}Irritated Heart Rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:32.73,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:33.89,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You need more calcium!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:34.64,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Have some mackerel!
